<h2><span><a href="http://www.top-perudo.com/top-perudo">	The Traits of a Top Perudo Player</a></span></h2>
<div>
<p>Do you often sit back and admire a table of professional Perudo players and wish that you could play half as well as them? Have you ever wondered what separates the constant winners from the constant losers in a game of Perudo? We take a look at what traits a truly top Perudo player possesses in the hope that it will inspire others to emulate these qualities.</p>
<p>In a game that relies so heavily on the art of bluffing and, yes, lying, it comes as no surprise that a top Perudo player, like a top online poker player, will undoubtedly be an excellent bluffer. It is not enough to simply bluff with words. Top players know that body language is an important part of the act and will not give away their bluff by stammering, averting eyes or mumbling. These Perudo players always look confident around the table and it is usually impossible to know when they are telling the truth and when they are bluffing.</p>
<p>In the same vein, a top online casino Perudo player will know how to read other players and know when they are bluffing. This takes a fair amount of skill and it can come naturally to some or only after years of experience. Knowing when to call a bluff is the mark of a true expert. Good Perudo players will also have excellent knowledge of the game&#8217;s rules and regulations. They will familiarize themselves with every element of the game through practice and play. These are the traits that good Perudo players ultimately possess.  </p>
